From lcollado at jhu.edu  Fri Jul 10 22:12:59 2015
From: lcollado at jhu.edu (Leonardo Collado Torres)
Date: Fri, 10 Jul 2015 16:12:59 -0400
Subject: [Bioc-devel] Memory issues with BiocParallel::SnowParam()
In-Reply-To: <CAANT7+WY5QPOy2q4JNBFyY8b2DM7BXPv08KawhnG-wWuqDazLQ@mail.gmail.com>
